text: Leslie Minnett (19 May 1883 - 8 August 1934) was an Australian cricketer. He played ten first-class matches for New South Wales between 1907/08 and 1914/15. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1883 births Category:1934 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
